# Vercel CLI artifacts
.vercel/

# Vercel serverless function bundle (built from vercel-handler/index.ts).
# Tracciato in git nonostante sia un build artifact: Vercel valida il
# pattern `functions` di vercel.json contro il git checkout PRE-build
# (https://vercel.link/unmatched-function-pattern). Senza api/index.js
# in git, ogni deploy fallisce in <1s con "pattern doesn't match any
# Serverless Functions". Tech debt residuo da rivedere al cutover.
